1882
01:50:26,750 --> 01:50:29,750
Sharon, I just called to tell you...
it's a tough world..

1883
01:50:30,250 --> 01:50:33,666
..but you have to be brave.

1884
01:50:34,166 --> 01:50:37,750
Let's not judge anyone.

1885
01:50:38,250 --> 01:50:41,875
