- Yeah.

1886
01:50:42,375 --> 01:50:45,875
Bye.

1887
01:50:48,375 --> 01:50:50,750
And the biggest breaking news of the hour.

1888
01:50:51,250 --> 01:50:52,625
Calendar Girl Paroma Ghosh..

