01:51:47,208 --> 01:51:47,458
Yes.

1910
01:51:47,958 --> 01:51:51,458
Your bail's been made.
Get ready and come out.

1911
01:52:02,541 --> 01:52:03,875
You will call us to Mumbai.

1912
01:52:04,375 --> 01:52:05,291
